  "title": "Trade Operation Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Assist to handle full spectrum of documentary trading transaction and deliver timely and quality service to support trading business.</li><li>Perform import & export documentations, includes L/C documentation with the terms and conditions.</li><li>Assist to liaise with bank on import & export documentation matters.</li><li>Work closely with internal counterparties for any discrepancy.</li><li>Provide support to senior on all trading transactions.</li><li>Maintain accurate trade transaction records.</li><li>Perform ad-hoc trade support duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>1-3 years of relevant experience preferred, those without experience are welcome to apply, on job training provided.</li><li>Familiar with the Microsoft Office and Oracle</li><li>Proficient in Mandarin to liaise with Chinese stakeholders.</li><li>Willing to learn, good interpersonal and communication skills.</li></ul>",
